## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

{% if language == 'nodejs' -%}
- Node.js 18+
- npm or yarn
{% elif language == 'python' -%}
- Python 3.11+
- pip
{% elif language == 'go' -%}
- Go 1.21+
{% endif -%}

### Environment Variables

{% if resourceType == 'database' -%}
```bash
DATABASE_HOST={{ name }}-db
DATABASE_PORT=5432
DATABASE_NAME={{ name }}
DATABASE_USER=<from-secret>
DATABASE_PASSWORD=<from-secret>
```
{% elif resourceType == 'bucket' -%}
```bash
GCS_BUCKET_NAME={{ name }}
```
{% endif -%}

### Installation

{% if language == 'nodejs' -%}
```bash
npm install
npm start
```
{% elif language == 'python' -%}
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
```
{% elif language == 'go' -%}
```bash
go run main.go
```
{% endif -%}

### Health Check

```bash
curl http://localhost:3000/health
```
